data.description: Welcome to this beautifully cared for 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch home nestled in a quiet neighborhood. This home, perfectly positioned on a spacious corner lot, offers a unique blend of modern upgrades and classic character. With a sunroom, family room, and living room, there is plenty of space to host the holidays. Outside, the generous corner lot presents ample space for gardening, outdoor entertaining, or simply enjoying the tranquility of the neighborhood. *This property qualifies for a $7500 GRANT, offered exclusively through Fairway Independent Mortgage Corp, for qualified buyers that meet the program criteria.
